1. what is Python :-

Python is a General Purpose, Simple, HLL, Dynamic, Object Oriented,
Extensible, Server Side,Interpreted and compiled scrpiting langauge.

General Purpose : a langauge which can used for any purpose. 
you can use python for web development, 
Enterprise Application, GUI Applications, Web Based Application, Emdedded Application, Data Application,
Intelligent System, IOT Use, Education college and school 9th and 10th Python CBSE and ICSE 
Python is All Rounder.
Simple : the langauage or syntax or rules of program in python is very easy, it is like writing English. it is easy to learn 
Even a Nursery Level or LKG Student Code in Python.

Eg:-
>>> print('Hi') if 5>6 else print('Hello')
Hello
>>> print('Hi') if 7>6 else print('Hello')
Hi
>>>
general languauge :-
=====================
1g : Binary Level or Machine Level
2g : Assembly Level 
3g : Mid Level (c,c++)
4g : HLL is 4rth generation (Programming English Like) (python,java,php,javascript)
5g : SQL is 5th generation

HLL : High Level Langauge 
C and Assembly, COBOL, FORTRAN 

Dynamic :-
=========
In Industry we have 2 types of PL 
1. Statically typed = type declaration is mendatory
2. Dynamically typed = type declaration is not mendatory
C/C++/Java langauge :-
int x = 20;
x = "Awnish" <----- it will give error.

Dynamically typed or Dynamic semantics.
x = 20 
x = True 
x = "Ravi"
Extensible:  Extend -> is there any chance of scalability or scope.
