Python is interpreted and compiled langauge 
java -> JVM (Java Virtual Machine)

.Java ---> code -> compile -> using javac -> 
bytecode --> .class --> jvm ---> execute.
due to this feature is java is said to be Plateform 
independent 

Python -> PVM (Python virtual Machine)
.py ---> code ---> compile ---> .pyc <compiled python code> -> bytecode -> execute -> 

python is also plateform Independent.
All Intepreted lanaguge are scripting in nature.

scripting language = Intepreted + Dynamic semantics
PHP = Intepreter + Dynamic
Javascript = Intepreter + Dynamic




